    "naive": "Find all my AAA patients.",
    "broad": "Find all AAA patients — by diagnosis (including ruptured) or by repair procedure (open or endovascular). Run multiple queries and union the patient sets.",
    "expert": "Run two queries. (1) Condition?code=http://snomed.info/sct|233985008,http://snomed.info/sct|14336007 — AAA dx variants. (2) Procedure?code=http://snomed.info/sct|24165007,http://snomed.info/sct|441788006 — AAA repair. Union the patient IDs."
  },
